  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The islands are growing restless, and its up to you to stop the leaders of each region from taking full control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast Paced Card Battling</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick your cards wisely, or just play the strongest ones you have! Take control of the stage and beat your opponents quickly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collection Focused</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover cool cards as you make your way through the islands. Any cards you find will be ready for you to play with on the next run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Neverending Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With 4 characters, and a multitude of cards, play the game how you want to play it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
